DESCRIPTION:<p><a href="https://www.wallyhood.org/2025/07/familyworks-30th-
 birthday-block-party-saturday-july-19th/">https://www.wallyhood.org/2025/07
 /familyworks-30th-birthday-block-party-saturday-july-19th/</a></p><p>Help u
 s celebrate 30 years of providing food\, support\, and resources to familie
 s in North Seattle by joining us for our 30th Birthday Block Party on <stro
 ng>Saturday\, July 19</strong>\, at <a href="https://familyworksseattle.us1
 4.list-manage.com/track/click?u=b80c1b083c64f284d5fbcda42&id=1f82512d4b&e=4
 5689f7eef" target="_blank"><b><u>Wallingford Presbyterian Church</u></b></a
 > from <strong>1–4 pm!</strong> We’ll have music\, snacks\, games\, kid-fri
 endly activities\, a visit from <a href="https://familyworksseattle.us14.li
 st-manage.com/track/click?u=b80c1b083c64f284d5fbcda42&id=8fdfd87432&e=45689
 f7eef" target="_blank"><b><u>Double Dutch Divas</u></b></a>\, and more!</p>
 <p>We can’t wait to see you there!</p><p><strong>Tickets are pay-what-you-c
 an.</strong> We’re excited to celebrate with our whole community\, and invi
 te you to choose the ticket price that’s right for you. <strong><u>If a $0 
 ticket makes it possible for you to attend\, you’re warmly encouraged to do
  so.</u></strong></p><p>If cost is not a barrier\, we suggest a ticket pric
 e of <strong>$30/ticket for adults</strong> and <strong>$15/ticket for yout
 h 12 and under.</strong> Contributions above that help cover the cost of fr
 ee tickets and make this celebration inclusive for all. <a href="https://fa
 milyworksseattle.us14.list-manage.com/track/click?u=b80c1b083c64f284d5fbcda
 42&id=2c36dc0c08&e=45689f7eef" target="_blank">Get tickets</a>.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250719T221744Z
LOCATION:Wallingford Presbyterian Church\, 1414 N 42nd St\, Seattle\, WA 98
 103\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:FamilyWorks 30th Birthday Block Party
