DESCRIPTION:Join us for an exciting night of brass music as <strong><b>Dall
 as Brass</b></strong> comes to Seattle on <strong><b>Friday\, January 16\, 
 2026 at 7:00pm</b></strong>. This concert features Dallas Brass in performa
 nce\, joined on stage by student musicians from <strong><b>Lincoln High Sch
 ool</b></strong> and <strong><b>Hamilton International Middle School</b></s
 trong>.  Get your tickets at: <strong><b><a href="https://tinyurl.com/dalla
 sbrasslhs" target="_blank">https://tinyurl.com/dallasbrasslhs</a></b></stro
 ng><br><h6 dir="ltr">General Admission / Adult 18-64 $25</h6><h6 dir="ltr">
 Student / Senior 65+ $20</h6><h6><span style="font-weight: normal\;">Known 
 for their energy\, musicianship\, and wide-ranging program\, Dallas Brass b
 rings together classical works\, jazz\, patriotic music\, and popular favor
 ites in a concert that appeals to all ages. The collaboration with our loca
 l school bands makes this a special evening celebrating music education and
  community.</span><br></h6><br>Lincoln High School Auditorium is accessible
  from the back of the school\,<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Li
 ncoln+High+School+Theater/@47.6599843\,-122.3398592\,18z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x
 549015c3d7c8cfab:0x5fc5b21281272c0b!8m2!3d47.6599857!4d-122.3388115!16s%2Fg
 %2F11kpm4ty_b?entry=ttu&amp\;g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDEwNy4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D"> on
  Woodlawn Avenue N between N 43rd and N 44th Streets.</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260113T032545Z
LOCATION:Lincoln High School Auditorium
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Lincoln High School hosting The Dallas Brass in concert
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
