 ttu&amp\;g_ep=EgoyMDI1MDkzMC4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D" target="_blank"><u>Wall
 ingford Center</u></a>.</p><p>What to expect:</p><ul><li><p dir="auto">We’l
 l provide litter pickers\, safety vests\, gloves\, and trash bags (and mayb
 e coffee and donuts too\, like the spring clean up!)</p></li><li><p dir="au
 to">We’ll be there\, rain or shine</p></li><li><p dir="auto">Families and f
 riends are welcome</p></li></ul><br><a href="https://www.wallyhood.org/2025
 /10/wallingford-neighborhood-cleanup-10-4/#gsc.tab=0">https://www.wallyhood
 .org/2025/10/wallingford-neighborhood-cleanup-10-4/#gsc.tab=0</a>
