DESCRIPTION:Thanks for your patience as we’ve made improvements to the buil
 ding.\n\nCome celebrate Member Appreciation Day with us! We’ll be providing
 \nlight refreshments and a chance to enter to win four tickets to Fremont O
 ktoberfest\, Sept. 18-20\, 2026.\n\nWe’re excited to celebrate you and the 
 community. Hope to see you there!\n\nNot a member? Join BECU and start expe
 riencing the credit union difference.
