DESCRIPTION:Room 202<br><br>Join us for an informative session on the state
 -mandated HB1110\, the “Middle Housing” legislation. We’ll delve into its d
 irect impact on Wallingford and its surrounding neighborhoods. The meeting 
 will feature a presentation and an open Q&amp\;A session\, where we’ll expl
 ore the legislation’s requirements for the city to permit 4-6 units on prev
 iously single-family lots outside the urban village in NR or neighborhood r
 esidential zones.<br><br><a href="https://www.wallingfordcc.org/2025/03/26/
 april-wcc-meeting-7-9-pm-zoning-proposals-feis-appeals-qa-memberships/">htt
 ps://www.wallingfordcc.org/2025/03/26/april-wcc-meeting-7-9-pm-zoning-propo
 sals-feis-appeals-qa-memberships/</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250426T230030Z
LOCATION:Good Shepherd Center\, 4649 Sunnyside Ave N\, Seattle\, WA 98103\,
  USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Wallingford Community Council General Meeting
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
