DESCRIPTION:Chapel (top floor of Good Shepherd Center)<br><br><strong>Featu
 red Speaker:</strong> Jorge Baron D4 representative on the King County Regi
 onal Council. (<a href="https://kingcounty.gov/en/dept/council/governance-l
 eadership/county-council/councilmembers-districts/jorge-l-baron/about" targ
 et="_blank">About Jorge Baron</a>)<br><br>If you would like to be considere
 d for nomination to a board member position\, please send a message describ
 ing your interest and past level of involvement with the neighborhood and W
 CC to <a href="mailto:communications@wallingfordcc.org" target="_blank">com
 munications@wallingfordcc.org</a> by April 20. Elected officers are Preside
 nt\, Vice President\, Secretary\, and three board members “at large”. The c
 urrent Treasurer is serving one more year of a two-year term.<br><br><a hre
 f="https://www.wallingfordcc.org/2025/03/26/april-wcc-meeting-7-9-pm-zoning
 -proposals-feis-appeals-qa-memberships/">https://www.wallingfordcc.org/2025
 /03/26/april-wcc-meeting-7-9-pm-zoning-proposals-feis-appeals-qa-membership
 s/</a>
