UID:2k8higuabr8vp6a8srqg8pttkb@google.com
CREATED:20250426T224153Z
DESCRIPTION:The event will be all day long\, from <strong><b>11:30 am to 10
 :00 pm</b></strong>\, and family-friendly\, with free root beer floats for 
 kids. There will also be door prizes\, live music\, and the release of an a
 nniversary white stout\, which is a collaboration with Spinnaker Chocolate 
 and Caffe Appassionato\, Figurehead’s future and current neighbors at each 
 of their two locations.<br><br><a href="https://www.wallyhood.org/2025/04/f
 igurehead-brewings-first-anniversary-party-april-19th/#gsc.tab=0">https://w
 ww.wallyhood.org/2025/04/figurehead-brewings-first-anniversary-party-april-
 19th/#gsc.tab=0</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250428T201830Z
LOCATION:Figurehead Stone Way\, 3513 Stone Way N\, Seattle\, WA 98103\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Figurehead Brewing's First Anniversary Party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
