CREATED:20250426T230756Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the 5th annual Tangletown PorchFest\, a unique and 
 free neighborhood music festival happening in Wallingford\, Seattle! Experi
 ence the vibrant local music scene as talented bands perform live on porche
 s throughout the Tangletown area. This family-friendly Seattle event brings
  the community together for an afternoon of live music and fun\, much like 
 a giant block party. Discover diverse genres\, support local artists\, and 
 enjoy one of Seattle's most beloved free music events. Check out our schedu
 le\, map\, and FAQs to plan your day at the Tangletown PorchFest\, a highli
 ght of the Wallingford-area community calendar.<br><br><a href="https://tan
 gletownporchfest.com">https://tangletownporchfest.com</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250625T045606Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Tangletown Porchfest
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
