DESCRIPTION:<p>Ticket price: $33.85</p><p><a href="https://www.eventbrite.c
 om/e/classical-persian-melodies-faraz-ensemble-tickets-1364544392009">https
 ://www.eventbrite.com/e/classical-persian-melodies-faraz-ensemble-tickets-1
 364544392009</a><br></p><p>Immerse yourself in the rich cultural heritage o
 f Iran as Faraz Ensemble presents a mesmerizing performance of classical Pe
 rsian music. Featuring the soulful sounds of the <strong><b><strong><b>Tar<
 /b></strong></b></strong>\, the haunting melodies of the <strong><b><strong
 ><b>Ney</b></strong></b></strong>\, the rhythmic beats of the <strong><b><s
 trong><b>Tombak</b></strong></b></strong>\, and the deep resonance of the <
 strong><b><strong><b>Cello</b></strong></b></strong>\, this ensemble will t
 ransport you to the heart of Iran.</p><p><strong><b><strong><b>Date:</b></s
 trong></b></strong> Saturday\, August 16\, 2025</p><p><strong><b><strong><b
 >Time:</b></strong></b></strong> 7:30 PM</p><p><strong><b><strong><b>Locati
 on:</b></strong></b></strong> <a href="https://historicseattle.org/project/
 good-shepherd/" target="_blank"><u><strong><b><strong><b>Good Shepherd Cent
 er</b></strong></b></strong></u></a><strong><b><strong><b>\, </b></strong><
 /b></strong>4649 Sunnyside Ave N\, Seattle\, WA 98103</p><p>Let Faraz Ensem
 ble transport you to the heart of Persia with their soul-stirring melodies 
 and captivating performances. Don't miss this opportunity to immerse yourse
 lf in the rich cultural heritage of Iran. See you there!</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250814T002837Z
LOCATION:Good Shepherd Center\, 4649 Sunnyside Avenue N\, Seattle\, WA 9810
 3
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Faraz Ensemble: Classical Persian Melodies
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
