DESCRIPTION:<p>A <strong><b>daffodil planting party</b></strong> is schedul
 ed for the morning of <strong><b>Saturday\, October 25\, starting at 10 am<
 /b></strong> and going as long as it takes to get the new bulbs into the gr
 ound. </p><p>Bring a hand spade if you have one\, and another to share. We’
 ll provide the bulbs and a little fertilizer.</p><p>If it is raining with i
 ntermittent showers we’ll still try to get the work done. If it is coming d
 own gully washers\, we’ll have the good sense to reschedule.</p><p><a href=
 "https://www.wallyhood.org/2025/10/daffodil-planting-party-at-wallingford-p
 layfield-saturday-october-25th/#gsc.tab=0">https://www.wallyhood.org/2025/1
 0/daffodil-planting-party-at-wallingford-playfield-saturday-october-25th/#g
 sc.tab=0</a><br></p>
