 nd Field #7</u></a> (near the bleachers)</p><p><em><i>SPS and SPR have agre
 ed to move forward with the track upgrades at Lower Woodland Field #7\, whi
 ch is owned by SPR. These improvements will support Lincoln’s robust track 
