DESCRIPTION:Starting at 10 am\, volunteers will gather at the southeast cor
 ner of N 45th Street and Wallingford Avenue N (across from QFC near Cascadi
 a Pharmacy). Supplies\, such as trash grabbers\, gloves\, trash bags\, and 
 safety vests will be available to help you safely beautify our neighborhood
 . The bi-annual clean up event is sponsored by the Wallingford Community Co
 uncil\, Historic Wallingford\, and the City of Seattle’s Adopt-a-Street pro
 gram. This is a family-friendly event\, and kids are welcome. The organizer
 s\, Will and Mike will be able to plan for your participation if you send a
 n RSVP to Will Vagel via Facebook messenger\, or send an email to <a href="
 mailto:wallingfordcleanup@gmail.com" target="_blank"><u>wallingfordcleanup@
 gmail.com</u></a>.<br><br><a href="https://www.wallyhood.org/2025/04/wallin
 gford-neighborhood-clean-up-is-on-saturday-april-19th/#gsc.tab=0">https://w
 ww.wallyhood.org/2025/04/wallingford-neighborhood-clean-up-is-on-saturday-a
 pril-19th/#gsc.tab=0</a>
