DESCRIPTION:The 2025 Fremont Solstice Parade kicks off at <b>3rd and Leary 
 Way</b>\, continues <b>along 36th Street</b>\, then turns right on <b>Evans
 ton Ave. N</b>\, taking a final right on <b>N 35th St</b>\, and finishing u
 p near the <b>Seattle Art Cars display inside the Fremont Fair</b> (see map
 ). Come be dazzled as more than 60 community- based ensembles parade down t
 he streets of Fremont with giant puppets\, stilt walkers\, floats\, dancers
 \, cyclists\, and musicians in this kaleidoscope of joyous human expression
 .<br><br><a href="https://fremontfair.com/solstice-parade/">https://fremont
 fair.com/solstice-parade/</a>
