DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>HOW TO ENTER</strong>:</p><ul><li><strong>In person<
 /strong>: Visit the Assistance League Thrift Store through November 29 to e
 nter. The beauty of buying your ticket at the store is that you get to see 
 the items in person\, plus you can see all the treasures the elves have put
  out this holiday season.<ul><li>The store is open <strong>Thursday and Fri
 day from 12–4 pm</strong>\, and <strong>Saturday from 10 am–4 pm</strong>.<
 /li></ul></li><li><strong>Online</strong>: On the Assistance League’s <a hr
 ef="https://www.assistanceleague.org/seattle/donate-2/" target="_blank"><u>
 Donate page</u></a>\, enter your information\, and in the “Is this a memori
 al or honorary gift?” field at the bottom of the page\, enter “Holiday Raff
 le.”</li><li><strong>Ticket price</strong>: $5 per ticket—buy multiple tick
 ets to increase your chances!</li><li><strong>Raffle date</strong>: Novembe
 r 29</li></ul><br><a href="https://www.wallyhood.org/2025/11/assistance-lea
 gue-crystal-mas-tree-raffle/">https://www.wallyhood.org/2025/11/assistance-
 league-crystal-mas-tree-raffle/</a>
