DESCRIPTION:The Sound and Fury Morris Dancers would like to invite all frie
 nds and neighbors to join us at dawn this Thursday (May 1) at Gas Works Par
 k for our annual May Day celebration. There will be song\, dance\, flowers\
 , and festivities! This is an outdoor\, family-friendly celebration with ro
 ots dating back centuries to the Cotswold region of England. It will be chi
 lly\, so please dress for the weather and feel free to bring a thermos\, la
 wn chairs\, blankets\, or whatever else would make you feel more comfortabl
 e.<br><br><a href="https://www.wallyhood.org/2025/04/annual-may-day-celebra
 tion-at-gasworks-park/">https://www.wallyhood.org/2025/04/annual-may-day-ce
 lebration-at-gasworks-park/</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250430T194406Z
LOCATION:Gas Works Park\, 2101 N Northlake Way\, Seattle\, WA 98103\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:May Day Celebration featuring Sound and Fury Morris Dancers
TRANSP:OPAQUE
